title: #92Noon!  9am Hour 7/26 - Starting New Again/QB Tier List/AFC East Action
description: PA & Nordo are LIVE from TCO discussing all of the changes around the team ahead of the start of training camp. PA reacts to a recent QB tier ranking & Kyler Murray's place on the list. Plus, PA highlights some AFC East action & goes down the schedule to predict win/loss totals for all four teams.
